Vincent A. WATSON et al. v. William C. SALOME, Jr., et al. No. 4029. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Jan. 24, 1950. Waldo B. Wetmore and Lawrence J. Wetzel, Wichita, Kan., for appellants. Lawrence E. Curfman, Fred W. Aley and Robert B. Morton, Wichita, Kan., for appellees.

Before BRATTON and PICKETT, Grcuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed January 24, 1950, on motion of appellants.
